HEADWORD: Fayalite
<hw>Fay"al*ite</hw> <pr>(f⟦amac⟧"⟦ait⟧l*⟦imac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[So called from the island <etsep>Fayal</etsep>.]</ety>
